title: 344. Andy, AJ & DJ CTI: Election Fraud In Colorado, Democrats Pressuring Disney To Run Abortion Ads & China's Warning To Nancy Pelosi
itunes:title: 344. Andy, AJ & DJ CTI: Election Fraud In Colorado, Democrats Pressuring Disney To Run Abortion Ads & China's Warning To Nancy Pelosi
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ are joined in the studio by AJ (@dreamrare). They discuss the election fraud that flipped the results in the Colorado election, Democrats pressuring Disney to run abortion ads on Hulu, and China's warning to Nancy Pelosi if she attempts to make a trip to Taiwan.
